{ for xml path

  The `path('RRR')` specifies the → development/XML tag with which each returned record is enclosed:
  gh|about-MSSQL|/sql/select/for-xml/path.sql||

}
{ Concatenation

  `for xml path` is useful to concatenate the »children« of a parent table.
  gh|about-MSSQL|/sql/select/for-xml/concatenation.sql||

}
